<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="391300000t" end="441700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">為了恢復一顆頭的我真是努力</p>
<p begin="441700000t" end="470000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">有身體真是太好了</p>
<p begin="477500000t" end="504600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">好了 感覺上我已經漂了很遠</p>
<p begin="504600000t" end="526300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">這裡究竟是哪裡呢</p>
<p begin="526300000t" end="544600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">千里眼</p>
<p begin="565000000t" end="580000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">是城鎮</p>
<p begin="587900000t" end="625000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">不知道那鎮上能不能討到食物吃</p>
<p begin="625000000t" end="653300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">應該沒辦法吧 畢竟我是蜘蛛</p>
<p begin="672100000t" end="686700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">那個是…</p>
<p begin="710400000t" end="735800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">是吸血鬼小孩搭乘的東西</p>
<p begin="776300000t" end="811300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">依然有很多人盯上那孩子啊</p>
<p begin="830000000t" end="861700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">警報響起 我的名字是"小蜘蛛"</p>
<p begin="861700000t" end="885900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(第十三集 好耶 是外面 我自由了嗎)</p>
<p begin="885900000t" end="891600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(第十三集 好耶 是外面 我自由了嗎)</p>
<p begin="891700000t" end="924200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">即使受挫跌倒也阻止不了我</p>
<p begin="924200000t" end="939600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">烏雲上吧</p>
<p begin="1048800000t" end="1073800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">有時候偶然會假裝成命中注定</p>
<p begin="1073800000t" end="1101300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">出現在善惡交會的立體透視街道</p>
<p begin="1101300000t" end="1130100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">惡夢在迷宮裡不過是家常便飯</p>
<p begin="1130100000t" end="1157500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">一般常識根本不管用</p>
<p begin="1157500000t" end="1208300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">用老套的正面進攻</p>
<p begin="1208300000t" end="1254100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">因為人生沒有你想得這麼簡單</p>
<p begin="1254200000t" end="1289190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">驅使我前進</p>
<p begin="1289190000t" end="1342500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">用這雙手創造勇敢的我</p>
<p begin="1342500000t" end="1365800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">「我最強 真是抱歉唷！」</p>
<p begin="1365800000t" end="1399100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">狂暴貪婪的蜘蛛乘風跳躍</p>
<p begin="1399200000t" end="1421700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">無法預測的新巨大波瀾</p>
<p begin="1448300000t" end="1477100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">還沒結束</p>
<p begin="1477100000t" end="1506300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">現在用最快的速度穿越黑暗</p>
<p begin="1506300000t" end="1538800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">因為人生只有一次</p>
<p begin="1538800000t" end="1569200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">只要直直向前跑</p>
<p begin="1569200000t" end="1634600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">解開纏繞在心頭的線</p>
<p begin="1634600000t" end="1702500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">就能跳到下一個興奮的舞台</p>
<p begin="1812100000t" end="1860400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">總算平安無事回來了</p>
<p begin="1868800000t" end="1890900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">沒想到竟然會被魔物拯救</p>
<p begin="1890900000t" end="1935400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">那一定是女神大人使喚的神獸大人</p>
<p begin="1935400000t" end="1982100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">一定是女神大人派來解救我們的</p>
<p begin="1982100000t" end="2011700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">神獸大人是嗎</p>
<p begin="2011700000t" end="2055500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">-老爺 要調查一下那隻蜘蛛魔物嗎</p>
<p begin="2055500000t" end="2078300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">-雖然我們才剛回來 拜託了</p>
<p begin="2078300000t" end="2096600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">我明白了</p>
<p begin="2096700000t" end="2121700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">有任何發現馬上告訴我</p>
<p begin="2390000000t" end="2422100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">老爺 出生了</p>
<p begin="2430400000t" end="2474200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">我的名字叫根岸彰子</p>
<p begin="2474200000t" end="2523400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">但是清醒後不知為何</p>
<p begin="2523400000t" end="2543700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">是健康的女寶寶</p>
<p begin="2558800000t" end="2583390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">真可愛</p>
<p begin="2583390000t" end="2599590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">聽好囉</p>
<p begin="2599590000t" end="2626700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">妳要成為像媽媽一樣的美女喔</p>
<p begin="2632100000t" end="2667100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">-要變得像爸爸一樣聰明喔 懂嗎</p>
<p begin="2667100000t" end="2707900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">但我似乎轉生成貴族的女兒</p>
<p begin="2719200000t" end="2758400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">為什麼會變成這樣</p>
<p begin="2758400000t" end="2809600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">我只記得我最後正在上古文課</p>
<p begin="2809600000t" end="2838400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">雖然一開始困惑又不安</p>
<p begin="2838400000t" end="2883700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">但是有溫柔的父母</p>
<p begin="2883800000t" end="2902100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">我很快就習慣了</p>
<p begin="2902100000t" end="2955000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">我本來以為可以像這樣自由自在</p>
<p begin="2955000000t" end="2974200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">直到那天為止…</p>
<p begin="2992900000t" end="3040000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">蘇菲亞 就快到家了 懂嗎</p>
<p begin="3040000000t" end="3081300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">蘇菲亞是我在這個世界的新名字</p>
<p begin="3081300000t" end="3125900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">不管怎麼說 我無法理解</p>
<p begin="3125900000t" end="3162500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">他們和我國的實力差距</p>
<p begin="3162500000t" end="3216700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">可能是和同盟國的連克山杜帝國</p>
<p begin="3216700000t" end="3258400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">有那兩個國家在背後撐腰</p>
<p begin="3258400000t" end="3325400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">神言教啊 聽說是他們促成</p>
<p begin="3325400000t" end="3381200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">因為他們認為女神教是邪教啊</p>
<p begin="3381300000t" end="3407100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">宗教的事情我不是很清楚</p>
<p begin="3407100000t" end="3467900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">按照他們的說法 神言教的國家</p>
<p begin="3467900000t" end="3490800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">但是神言教的教義是說</p>
<p begin="3490800000t" end="3530000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">"如果想聽到神的聲音</p>
<p begin="3530000000t" end="3575000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">那與"等級提升了"的系統音效</p>
<p begin="3575000000t" end="3612900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">居然信奉那個聲音</p>
<p begin="3652100000t" end="3679200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">老爺 請在車內等候</p>
<p begin="3739600000t" end="3756300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">殺了他們</p>
<p begin="3869600000t" end="3887500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">什…什麼</p>
<p begin="3913800000t" end="3929200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">蜘蛛</p>
<p begin="3929200000t" end="3945000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">魔…魔物</p>
<p begin="3965800000t" end="3984600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">快…快逃</p>
<p begin="4017500000t" end="4050000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">這個世界竟然有那種怪物</p>
<p begin="4059600000t" end="4084200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">郊外好可怕</p>
<p begin="4084200000t" end="4142100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">再怎麼樣牠都不可能進入城鎮</p>
<p begin="4197100000t" end="4220900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">有什麼事嗎</p>
<p begin="4220900000t" end="4238700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">老爺</p>
<p begin="4238800000t" end="4248400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">怎麼了</p>
<p begin="4248400000t" end="4296600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">那隻蜘蛛魔物好像在近郊的森林</p>
<p begin="4296700000t" end="4313800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">你說什麼</p>
<p begin="4362100000t" end="4385000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">我們在此別過吧</p>
<p begin="4385000000t" end="4401700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">多謝關照</p>
<p begin="4417100000t" end="4457100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">不過我真的可以把地龍的材料</p>
<p begin="4457100000t" end="4477900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">如果賣掉可以大賺一票喔</p>
<p begin="4477900000t" end="4517900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">因為旅程有點趕</p>
<p begin="4528300000t" end="4554100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">那我就不客氣收下了</p>
<p begin="4563300000t" end="4617500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">那個…巴斯卡先生</p>
<p begin="4617500000t" end="4657900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">少年 我只是微不足道的嚮導…</p>
<p begin="4675400000t" end="4713300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">帶領你們來到這裡是我的職責</p>
<p begin="4713300000t" end="4746600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">接下來要靠你們自己</p>
<p begin="4746700000t" end="4779200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">沒有我這種老頭出場的餘地</p>
<p begin="4792500000t" end="4838800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">我會祈禱世界稍微好轉一點</p>
<p begin="4880800000t" end="4906200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">我會竭盡所能的</p>
<p begin="4933300000t" end="4962500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">我們會直接通往精靈的村落嗎</p>
<p begin="4962500000t" end="4997900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">進入村落前必須經過沙利艾拉國</p>
<p begin="4997900000t" end="5040400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">因此我們要先到附近的村子</p>
<p begin="5040400000t" end="5078700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">對喔 菲的翅膀太顯眼了</p>
<p begin="5078800000t" end="5097600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">這也是其中一點</p>
<p begin="5097600000t" end="5137500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">但最大的理由是宗教上的問題</p>
<p begin="5137500000t" end="5172100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">沙利艾拉國是信仰女神的國家</p>
<p begin="5172100000t" end="5208800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">據說女神擁有白色的翅膀…</p>
<p begin="5208800000t" end="5240490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">意思是看到菲的翅膀</p>
<p begin="5240490000t" end="5259200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">如果是那樣倒還好</p>
<p begin="5259200000t" end="5307100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">但也有可能會被當成</p>
<p begin="5323300000t" end="5370000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">也就是說根據思考方式不同</p>
<p begin="5370000000t" end="5412900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">女神教的教義是</p>
<p begin="5412900000t" end="5463300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">但是神言教的教義卻是</p>
<p begin="5463300000t" end="5478300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">獻上技能</p>
<p begin="5478300000t" end="5500800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">聽說他們有"消除技能"這項技能</p>
<p begin="5500800000t" end="5553300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">他們似乎認為這樣消除的技能</p>
<p begin="5553300000t" end="5616600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">就像擁有轉生前記憶的我們</p>
<p begin="5616700000t" end="5631700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">兩邊都很可疑啊</p>
<p begin="5631700000t" end="5686700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">是啊 女神教和神言教彼此將對方</p>
<p begin="5686700000t" end="5717500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">以前還打過仗喔</p>
<p begin="5717500000t" end="5785400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">修雖然不是神言教徒</p>
<p begin="5785400000t" end="5836700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">也就是說要是勇者的身分洩露</p>
<p begin="5836700000t" end="5863400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">最好還是不要引人注目</p>
<p begin="5863400000t" end="5878300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">說得也是</p>
<p begin="5906700000t" end="5935000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">沒有更可愛的款式嗎</p>
<p begin="5935000000t" end="5957500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">粉紅色或點點圖案的</p>
<p begin="5957500000t" end="5974600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">妳又不能引人注目</p>
<p begin="5974600000t" end="5995400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">我也知道啊</p>
<p begin="5995400000t" end="6052500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">獻上技能吧 這樣就能得救</p>
<p begin="6066700000t" end="6117500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">雖說神言教已經落入由古手中</p>
<p begin="6117500000t" end="6174200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">神言教的教皇達斯汀</p>
<p begin="6185800000t" end="6204100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">教皇啊</p>
<p begin="6221300000t" end="6254600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">修有見過教皇嗎</p>
<p begin="6254600000t" end="6278800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">-有…</p>
<p begin="6278800000t" end="6316300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">很好…不哭不哭 真了不起</p>
<p begin="6360800000t" end="6406200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">願神保佑你</p>
<p begin="6453300000t" end="6476600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">他看起來是善良的人</p>
<p begin="6489600000t" end="6552500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">如果那個人也被洗腦 被利用的話</p>
<p begin="6552500000t" end="6592500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">是啊 為了救他我們趕快走吧</p>
<p begin="6642100000t" end="6691700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">女神教…神言教…兩邊都不可信</p>
<p begin="6697900000t" end="6735000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">必須靠我們自己的力量打敗由古</p>
<p begin="6741300000t" end="6776300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">新任勇者由古‧邦恩‧連克山杜</p>
<p begin="6776300000t" end="6809200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">為了討伐邪惡的精靈出兵了</p>
<p begin="6920000000t" end="6966300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">就讓由古好好替我們賣命吧</p>
<p begin="7394200000t" end="7433400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">新技能 名字叫千里咒怨邪眼</p>
<p begin="7433400000t" end="7471600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">從超遠的距離</p>
<p begin="7471700000t" end="7499600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">連我都畏懼自己的力量</p>
<p begin="7499600000t" end="7554200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">如果家裡出現屍體的話</p>
<p begin="7554200000t" end="7601300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">好不容易得救了又立刻被殺掉</p>
<p begin="7615800000t" end="7672500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">來看看被做記號的傢伙</p>
<p begin="7754600000t" end="7781300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">是精靈嗎 原來是精靈啊</p>
<p begin="7781300000t" end="7805100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">好像在說明什麼</p>
<p begin="7848300000t" end="7889600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">自言自語 不對 是心靈感應啊</p>
<p begin="7889600000t" end="7924600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">不過沒想到暴徒竟然是精靈啊</p>
<p begin="7924600000t" end="7987900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">精靈的形象…</p>
<p begin="7987900000t" end="8030000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">在那裡的精靈身上連清廉的</p>
<p begin="8030000000t" end="8086300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">而且之前攻擊吸血鬼小孩的盜賊們</p>
<p begin="8086300000t" end="8105100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">為什麼要盯上她呢</p>
<p begin="8130000000t" end="8180800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">反正會上賊船肯定有什麼好處</p>
<p begin="8180800000t" end="8206600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">我就守護他們吧</p>
<p begin="8206700000t" end="8256300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">幸好不知道為什麼</p>
<p begin="8256300000t" end="8297600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">從那裡到這裡 即便是魔王</p>
<p begin="8297600000t" end="8336300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">暫時在這裡落腳一陣子也沒問題</p>
<p begin="8352900000t" end="8390800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">總之今天就到這裡 晚安</p>
<p begin="8407100000t" end="8423800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">失敗</p>
<p begin="8423800000t" end="8433800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">是</p>
<p begin="8433800000t" end="8450500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">理由呢</p>
<p begin="8450500000t" end="8485400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">兩次都被蜘蛛魔物妨礙</p>
<p begin="8485400000t" end="8513700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">說是巧合未免也太巧了</p>
<p begin="8513800000t" end="8547600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">那麼…今後該怎麼做呢</p>
<p begin="8547600000t" end="8574200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">我親自出馬</p>
<p begin="8574200000t" end="8594600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">波狄瑪斯大人要親自出馬</p>
<p begin="8594600000t" end="8651300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">不要放鬆對那隻蜘蛛的監視</p>
<p begin="8673300000t" end="8715800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">蜘蛛魔物…是愛麗兒的眷屬嗎</p>
<p begin="8715800000t" end="8760000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">轉生者存在這件事</p>
<p begin="8760000000t" end="8817500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">不只愛麗兒</p>
<p begin="8817500000t" end="8858300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">雖然我一直想盡辦法別讓他察覺</p>
<p begin="8858300000t" end="8918300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">地點太糟了 肯連領地</p>
<p begin="8918300000t" end="8955400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">達斯汀是否注意到轉生者的存在</p>
<p begin="8955400000t" end="8996700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">但我們如果繼續大膽行動</p>
<p begin="9002900000t" end="9044600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">最壞的情況</p>
<p begin="9044600000t" end="9090400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">愛麗兒擁有強大的力量</p>
<p begin="9090400000t" end="9115000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">不管對上哪邊都很麻煩</p>
<p begin="9125400000t" end="9190000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">不過這也是個好機會</p>
<p begin="9233800000t" end="9242600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">睜眼</p>
<p begin="9242600000t" end="9267900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">好了 今天也打起精神上吧</p>
<p begin="9267900000t" end="9303700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">去盡情四處獵殺盜賊吧</p>
<p begin="9332500000t" end="9386300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">儀式 在祈禱嗎</p>
<p begin="9422500000t" end="9457100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">很好 照這股氣勢繼續殺吧</p>
<p begin="9462100000t" end="9485000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">他們又在祈禱</p>
<p begin="9485000000t" end="9505400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">可是無論再怎麼向神禱告</p>
<p begin="9505400000t" end="9542100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">也無法改變將被滅族的事實喔</p>
<p begin="9595000000t" end="9660400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">這個世界的盜賊都像那樣嗎</p>
<p begin="9660400000t" end="9685000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">連精靈都跑去當盜賊</p>
<p begin="9685000000t" end="9730400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">說不定我在不知情的情況下</p>
<p begin="9730400000t" end="9762500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">跟監 偽裝成盜賊的某國間諜們</p>
<p begin="9762500000t" end="9775400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">開玩笑的啦</p>
<p begin="9791300000t" end="9833000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">這樣啊 意思是諜報部隊全滅嗎</p>
<p begin="9833000000t" end="9841200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">是</p>
<p begin="9841300000t" end="9900100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">從變裝的間諜沒有被殺這點研判</p>
<p begin="9911700000t" end="9947500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">半路殺出程咬金啊</p>
<p begin="9947500000t" end="10001700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">沒想到迷宮惡夢</p>
<p begin="10001700000t" end="10039200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">牠是有愛麗兒大人撐腰的魔物</p>
<p begin="10039200000t" end="10077500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">是想警告我們別對沙利艾拉國出手嗎</p>
<p begin="10077500000t" end="10123800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">不管怎麼樣都只能繼續警戒然後視察</p>
<p begin="10123800000t" end="10165100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">而且要防備的還不只愛麗兒大人</p>
<p begin="10165100000t" end="10202100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">其他的盜賊是哪邊派來的</p>
<p begin="10202100000t" end="10255000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">好像是在世界各國頻繁活動的</p>
<p begin="10255000000t" end="10304200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">我們還掌握了那個組織裡</p>
<p begin="10304200000t" end="10363390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">臭波狄瑪斯 那男人的所作所為</p>
<p begin="10363390000t" end="10379600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">報告還沒完</p>
<p begin="10379600000t" end="10425890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">肯連領地裡還有精靈出沒 要除掉嗎</p>
<p begin="10425890000t" end="10464100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">波狄瑪斯盯上肯連領地的目的</p>
<p begin="10464200000t" end="10503800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">還有在各地發生的人頭買賣也是</p>
<p begin="10503800000t" end="10537600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">拐走大量的孩子究竟要做什麼</p>
<p begin="10537600000t" end="10555000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">不 其實相反嗎</p>
<p begin="10555000000t" end="10605000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">是為了不讓人察覺</p>
<p begin="10605000000t" end="10630800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">情報太少了</p>
<p begin="10630800000t" end="10645000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">達斯汀大人</p>
<p begin="10654600000t" end="10675400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">不 先放過他們</p>
<p begin="10675400000t" end="10702100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">現在的當務之急是擊潰女神教</p>
<p begin="10702100000t" end="10714200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">是</p>
<p begin="10714200000t" end="10762100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">不要放鬆監視 要當成已經開戰</p>
<p begin="10762100000t" end="10779200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">我明白了</p>
<p begin="10793800000t" end="10838800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">要是愛麗兒大人和波狄瑪斯</p>
<p begin="10838800000t" end="10913000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">肯連領地的領主一直都極力避免戰爭</p>
<p begin="10913000000t" end="10945400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">甚至不知道是我們一步步誘導的</p>
<p begin="10945400000t" end="11009600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">女神教討厭神言教</p>
<p begin="11009600000t" end="11061300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">明明兩邊信奉的是同樣的神明</p>
<p begin="11061300000t" end="11087100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">這究竟是怎麼回事</p>
<p begin="11087100000t" end="11149600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">雖然加派了盜賊繼續前來誘拐</p>
<p begin="11149600000t" end="11173800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">是被那隻蜘蛛魔物解決掉的嗎</p>
<p begin="11173800000t" end="11192100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">恐怕是…</p>
<p begin="11192100000t" end="11233800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">我太太在鎮上到處鼓吹那隻魔物</p>
<p begin="11233800000t" end="11279200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">百姓開始深信那是神獸大人了吧</p>
<p begin="11279200000t" end="11304600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">完全不知道我多操心</p>
<p begin="11304600000t" end="11324200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">就算被稱為神獸大人</p>
<p begin="11324200000t" end="11364600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">真實身分還是從艾爾羅大迷宮</p>
<p begin="11364600000t" end="11406700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">在歐茲國被稱為"迷宮惡夢"</p>
<p begin="11406700000t" end="11449600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">我聽說歐茲國的要塞一瞬間</p>
<p begin="11449600000t" end="11475000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">危險度高達S級</p>
<p begin="11475000000t" end="11536700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">可是從只攻擊盜賊這點來看</p>
<p begin="11536700000t" end="11570500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">可以解讀人語 甚至進行交談</p>
<p begin="11570500000t" end="11610800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">就算擁有很高的智慧</p>
<p begin="11610800000t" end="11655800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">你有自信能和神言教的人們</p>
<p begin="11673800000t" end="11699200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">你對惡夢有什麼看法</p>
<p begin="11699200000t" end="11735900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">這個嘛…我也不知道</p>
<p begin="11735900000t" end="11785800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">應該說牠難以捉摸嗎</p>
<p begin="11798800000t" end="11839600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">邪惡卻行俠仗義…</p>
<p begin="11844600000t" end="11857100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">不好了</p>
<p begin="11857100000t" end="11876700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">怎麼了 吵什麼吵</p>
<p begin="11876700000t" end="11905000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">惡夢救了重病患者</p>
<p begin="11905000000t" end="11941300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">那隻蜘蛛是怎麼回事啊</p>
<p begin="11941300000t" end="11985100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">看來這附近的盜賊已經死光了</p>
<p begin="11985100000t" end="12047100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">領主似乎把我當成危險分子</p>
<p begin="12047100000t" end="12090400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">不過夫人倒是對我抱持著好感</p>
<p begin="12090400000t" end="12135400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">看來這座城鎮信奉的女神教裡</p>
<p begin="12135400000t" end="12197500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">蜘蛛是神聖的生物 是女神的使者</p>
<p begin="12197500000t" end="12274600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">我記得某個魔王好像也一樣</p>
<p begin="12274600000t" end="12335400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">我確實是魔王的親戚</p>
<p begin="12335400000t" end="12383300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">不過照女神教的說法</p>
<p begin="12383300000t" end="12409600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">還是不要繼續多想比較好</p>
<p begin="12420000000t" end="12432100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">有人來了</p>
<p begin="12439200000t" end="12495000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">神獸大人 請您…</p>
<p begin="12495000000t" end="12559600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">要我救他 但我又不是神獸</p>
<p begin="12577900000t" end="12610400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">我就盡全力試試看吧</p>
<p begin="12653800000t" end="12705900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">肝臟癌…明明還這麼小</p>
<p begin="12705900000t" end="12732900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">(劣食)</p>
<p begin="12747500000t" end="12774600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">(營養失調 肌肉與內臟功能很差)</p>
<p begin="12774600000t" end="12790900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">求求您</p>
<p begin="12790900000t" end="12817900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">反正我很閒 就治好他們吧</p>
<p begin="12920400000t" end="12994200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">感謝我吧 然後以此為教訓</p>
<p begin="13010000000t" end="13045000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">謝禮 討厭 你們也會做好事嘛</p>
<p begin="13045000000t" end="13064600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">-謝謝</p>
<p begin="13321700000t" end="13356300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">煩死了！煩死了！我敢肯定是我贏！</p>
<p begin="13356300000t" end="13386300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">弱肉(吞噬)強食(殆盡！)</p>
<p begin="13386300000t" end="13421300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">"再來！再來！"真是無聊的遊戲</p>
<p begin="13421300000t" end="13452600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">可別給我小看人生啊？</p>
<p begin="13452600000t" end="13487500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">哎呀哎呀 上當了啊！</p>
<p begin="13487500000t" end="13520800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">上了低等生物的當是什麼感覺？</p>
<p begin="13520800000t" end="13549600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">今天依舊幸災樂禍以下犯上</p>
<p begin="13549600000t" end="13584600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">沒道理…倒楣…那又怎麼樣！</p>
<p begin="13584600000t" end="13645900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">給我用盡全力活下去！！！</p>
<p begin="13645900000t" end="13680000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">成功了！！！</p>
<p begin="13680000000t" end="13711300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">控絲 毒牙 必勝戰術 給我走著瞧www</p>
<p begin="13711300000t" end="13745900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">勝利了！！！已經無人能阻止我</p>
